      "content": "it just feels selfish to keep holding on when i know their lives would be so much lighter without the constant chaos i bring. like, isn't it actually more loving to just... step aside? to give them the chance to be happy without having to worry about me all the time? it feels like the only way i can actually do something good for them is to stop being the problem.",
